# Execution logs under logs/ are intentionally TRACKED (committed) for review/audit —
# pod stdout, NCCL traces, benchmark results, and run orchestration logs are kept in-repo
# so past runs are reviewable. (Previously these were ignored.)
!logs/.gitkeep
